channel.title: Server developer looking for team/project
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape community. I am looking to join a 317 project/team. I have been developing 317's since 2009. I have mostly been doing it for the learning experience but now would like to make a high quality server with others.
If you have a current project or want to start a project feel free to private message me or skype me.
My skype is [b]coding.content[/b]
Message me your moparscape name and some information about your project for me to accept your friend request.
Thanks Again!
-Team Player
